    <item>
      <title>调查显示德国经济陷入衰退，2024 年将无增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/german-economy-in-recession-with-no-more-growth-seen-in-2024</link>
      <description><![CDATA[彭博社的一项调查显示，德国正遭受轻度经济衰退，2024 年全年的产出将持平——凸显了欧洲最大经济体的萎靡不振。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-14/german-economy-in-recession-with-no-more-growth-seen-in-2024</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 14 Oct 2024 04:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国就以色列与伊朗冲突举行新闻发布会 油价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-14</link>
      <description><![CDATA[受以色列袭击伊朗的阴影笼罩市场的影响，中国财政部周六召开了备受期待的新闻发布会，会上未提及任何刺激措施以刺激中国这一最大进口国的消费，导致油价下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-13/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-oct-14</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 13 Oct 2024 22:13:41 GMT</pubDate>
